# Sentinel Suite — Authors & Contributors

The people whose work is in the Sentinel Suite. If you contributed and released
your work for open-source use under this project, you belong here.

## Maintainer / primary author
- silentsudo-io  — Sentinel runtime, sensors, Council, Deck/Bridge, safety
  substrate, dashboard/cockpit, and the overall suite design.

## Contributors (released for open-source use, with permission)
Contributors are credited **in the source file(s) they authored or worked on** —
in that file's header comment and/or changelog — so each grant stays attached to
the exact code it covers. Look there for per-file attribution.

